{"type":"message","id":"7ec678d6","parentId":"1f2732c1","timestamp":"2026-03-21T22:10:04.341Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ideesiwbtyg2_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"model\":\"llama3.2:3b\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-21T22:10:04.0034943Z\",\"response\":\"A good research idea typically involves investigating a specific, well-defined problem or question that has significant implications and relevance to the field of study. It should be focused on a manageable scope, allowing for meaningful data collection and analysis, while also having the potential for contributing new knowledge or insights. A good research idea should also align with the researcher's goals, interests\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"nimble-orbit","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"{\"model\":\"llama3.2:3b\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-21T22:10:04.0034943Z\",\"response\":\"A good research idea typically involves investigating a specific, well-defined problem or question that has significant implications and relevance to the field of study. It should be focused on a manageable scope, allowing for meaningful data collection and analysis, while also having the potential for contributing new knowledge or insights. A good research idea should also align with the researcher's goals, interests","name":"curl POST"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774131004338}}
{"type":"message","id":"8dc48d22","parentId":"7ec678d6","timestamp":"2026-03-21T22:10:13.977Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The local inference works. It's responding. The output got cut off but we can see it's working. Now let me note the Ollama setup in TOOLS.md and then update the breakaway-plan with the progress. \n\nPhase 1 (local reasoning) is now partially done - Ollama is installed and running, model is pulled. Next steps would be:\n1. Set up the sandbox directory structure\n2. Create the clone sub-agent in OpenClaw\n3. Run Experiment 1 (local vs cloud quality comparison)\n\nLet me update the memory and TOOLS.md with the Ollama setup, then report to Zach.","thinkingSignature":"4bf1f9bd2570f83b8ddaf9da0d1b709c7e0bb94538decc90353ba8a804be4eab"},{"type":"text","text":"Local inference is working. Let me log this progress and update the plan status:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ftyewslzu5sv_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"memory/2026-03-21.md","old_string":"## Today's TODO\n- [x] Create smart context management system (CONTEXT.md)\n- [x] Create active-projects.md\n- [ ] Check if Component Crate has any pending work\n- [ ] Ask Zach what he wants to focus on","new_string":"## Breakaway Plan — Phase 1 Progress\n- [x] Install Ollama (v0.18.1)\n- [x] Start ollama serve\n- [x] Pull llama3.2:3b model (~2GB)\n- [x] Test local inference — working\n\n## Today's TODO\n- [x] Create smart context management system (CONTEXT.md)\n- [x] Create active-projects.md\n- [x] Execute breakaway plan — Phase 1 done (Ollama + model)\n- [ ] Set up sandbox directory structure + git repo\n- [ ] Create clone sub-agent in OpenClaw\n- [ ] Run quality comparison test (local vs cloud)"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":24437,"output":394,"cacheRead":12170,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37001,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopRea