{"type":"message","id":"c9aa5f12","parentId":"f94fdcc8","timestamp":"2026-03-21T22:10:27.416Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me update TOOLS.md with the Ollama info.","thinkingSignature":"ef84c39ff2d6f5da0bdbad59f6c9bbba59d55211a3f9268defea72fa2d104a58"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ibfhbl3oi1zd_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"TOOLS.md","old_string":"## Why Separate?\n\nSkills are shared. Your setup is yours. Keeping them apart means you can update skills without losing your notes, and share skills without leaking your infrastructure.\n\n---\n\nAdd whatever helps you do your job. This is your cheat sheet.","new_string":"## Why Separate?\n\nSkills are shared. Your setup is yours. Keeping them apart means you can update skills without losing your notes, and share skills without leaking your infrastructure.\n\n---\n\nAdd whatever helps you do your job. This is your cheat sheet.\n\n## Local LLM (Breakaway Sandbox)\n\n**Ollama:** `ollama serve` (v0.18.1) running on localhost:11434\n**Model:** llama3.2:3b (2GB, pulled 2026-03-21)\n**Test command:** `curl -X POST http://localhost:11434/api/generate -d '{\"model\":\"llama3.2:3b\",\"prompt\":\"...\",\"stream\":false}'`"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":25364,"output":259,"cacheRead":12170,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37793,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774131020922}}
