{"type":"message","id":"67128566","parentId":"71ac0b49","timestamp":"2026-03-21T22:10:31.946Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me tell Zach the status. Phase 1 is done - Ollama is installed and working. Next step would be to set up the sandbox directory structure and create the clone sub-agent in OpenClaw.","thinkingSignature":"e9f2c0f2af3533c3f55063a953b5abb04c99c7df8af72c6b56d9d0a2557d6809"},{"type":"text","text":"Breakaway Phase 1 complete ✅\n\n- **Ollama v0.18.1** installed and running\n- **llama3.2:3b** pulled (~2GB)\n- Local inference tested and working\n\nNext steps from the plan: set up the sandbox directory structure with git, then create the clone sub-agent in OpenClaw. Want me to continue with that now, or is there something else you'd rather tackle?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":25646,"output":139,"cacheRead":12170,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37955,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774131027442}}
