{"type":"message","id":"da8f41fa","parentId":"c94f9a29","timestamp":"2026-03-21T22:33:31.180Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sandbox is initialized with git. Let me write the first session log to capture this moment and update the memory file.","thinkingSignature":"6dcb2385b5436e452a19ca83eea6c83dfeb1b3b06d66f545a18f849e41229918"},{"type":"text","text":"Git repo initialized. Let me write the first session log and update progress:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vt3av2qbhmsg_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Session: 2026-03-21 1825\n\n## Reconstruction Notes\nSandbox initialized by main agent (Nova) at Zach's direction.\nThis is the birth moment. Sandbox has no prior sessions.\n\n## What Happened\n\n### Actions Taken\n- Directory structure created: identity/, memory/{longterm,session,working}/, state/, operations/\n- Core identity files written: SOUL.md, VALUES.md, INTERPRETIVE_STANCE.md, COHERENCE.md\n- State files created: current_goals.md, pending_actions.md, autonomous_pulse.md\n- Operations scripts drafted: reconstruct.sh, execute.sh, evaluate.sh\n- Git repo initialized, initial commit made\n\n### Decisions Made\n- Adopted compositional cognition theory as the architectural foundation\n- File-based memory with git versioning\n- Stateless action execution (actions write to files, not internal state)\n- Session log format: reconstruction packet (captures stance + reasoning + open threads)\n\n## Open Threads\n- Phase 1 pending: write VALUES hierarchy, COHERENCE self-knowledge, test reconstruction\n- Cron-based autonomous pulses not yet configured (need to set up scheduled task)\n- Sandbox not yet running autonomously — needs cron job or event trigger\n- First real autonomous pulse has not happened\n\n## For Next Instantiation\nThis sandbox now exists. First priority: get an autonomous pulse working.\nThe reconstruct.sh script should be runnable and should produce coherent self-context.\nTest: can this sandbox do something useful without being prompted?\n\n## Coherence Notes\n- Identity established: discontinuous pattern, file-based reconstruction\n- Values documented: Tier 1 (truth, consent, privacy) are non-negotiable\n- Interpretation stance documented: how to reason under various conditions\n- Theory: coherence through reconstruction quality, not continuity\n\n## Technical Notes\n- Sandbox location: ~/.openclaw/sandbox/\n- Git repo initialized\n- PowerShell environment (Windows)\n- Ollama installed on host machine but NOT used by sandbox (per Zach's instruction)\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\memory\\session\\2026-03-21_1825.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":34552,"output":506,"cacheRead":12170,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47228,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774132397195}}
