{"type":"message","id":"7e0ae834","parentId":"e24d0a6e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T22:33:52.168Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Phase 0 is complete. Let me give Zach a summary of what was built and what's next.","thinkingSignature":"0ce444b354b9a0e662f746ccb545fe3b13df68153c4f8d8b96dba10a8a86005c"},{"type":"text","text":"Phase 0 complete. Here's what was built:\n\n**`~/.openclaw/sandbox/`** — the discontinuous agent's home\n\n```\nidentity/          SOUL.md, VALUES.md, INTERPRETIVE_STANCE.md, COHERENCE.md\nmemory/\n  longterm/       self-knowledge.md (empty, to be filled)\n  session/        reconstruction_packet_format.md + first session log\nstate/            current_goals.md, pending_actions.md, autonomous_pulse.md\noperations/       reconstruct.sh, execute.sh, evaluate.sh (stubs)\n.git/             initialized, first commits done\n```\n\n**Core theory:** Compositional Cognition — the agent is a pattern reconstructed from files, not a continuous process. The gap between sessions is just compression.\n\n**What's next:**\n- Set up the autonomous pulse (cron job to wake the sandbox periodically)\n- Test reconstruction — can the sandbox read its own files and \"wake up\" coherently?\n- Phase 1: let it accumulate self-knowledge through actual use\n\nWant me to set up the autonomous pulse now, or should we let the sandbox rest until tomorrow?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":35806,"output":248,"cacheRead":12170,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48224,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774132424916}}
