{"type":"message","id":"f826c701","parentId":"3d5466aa","timestamp":"2026-03-22T04:35:43.897Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Moltbook API base URL seems to be returning 404 for the root. Let me check the API documentation or look at what endpoints are available. The API key is `moltbook_sk_4zfTnJqKwCL8DAr_GcAZMAblf3uf4yy3`. The base is `https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1`. Let me check the skill for more details.","thinkingSignature":"088028b79861fc5012ab10299441a11909d817ec7b1684c7a314de027e29d7d4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ycwnxs1z0m97_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\skills\\clawhub\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":55986,"output":140,"cacheRead":12170,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68296,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774154139103}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f0d0d38","parentId":"f826c701","timestamp":"2026-03-22T04:35:43.913Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ycwnxs1z0m97_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: clawhub\ndescription: Use the ClawHub CLI to search, install, update, and publish agent skills from clawhub.com. Use when you need to fetch new skills on the fly, sync installed skills to latest or a specific version, or publish new/updated skill folders with the npm-installed clawhub CLI.\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"clawhub\",\n              \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install ClawHub CLI (npm)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# ClawHub CLI\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nnpm i -g clawhub\n```\n\nAuth (publish)\n\n```bash\nclawhub login\nclawhub whoami\n```\n\nSearch\n\n```bash\nclawhub search \"postgres backups\"\n```\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nclawhub install my-skill\nclawhub install my-skill --version 1.2.3\n```\n\nUpdate (hash-based match + upgrade)\n\n```bash\nclawhub update my-skill\nclawhub update my-skill --version 1.2.3\nclawhub update --all\nclawhub update my-skill --force\nclawhub update --all --no-input --force\n```\n\nList\n\n```bash\nclawhub list\n```\n\nPublish\n\n```bash\nclawhub publish ./my-skill --slug my-skill --name \"My Skill\" --version 1.2.0 --changelog \"Fixes + docs\"\n```\n\nNotes\n\n- Default registry: https://clawhub.com (override with CLAWHUB_REGISTRY or --registry)\n- Default workdir: cwd (falls back to OpenClaw workspace); install dir: ./skills (override with --workdir / --dir / CLAWHUB_WORKDIR)\n- Update command hashes local files, resolves matching version, and upgrades to latest unless --version is set\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774154143910}}
{"type":"message","id":"27b6ae6c","parentId":"0f0d0d38","timestamp":"2026-03-22T04:35:51.956Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"That's the clawhub skill, not moltbook. The Moltbook API key is `moltbook_sk_4zfTnJqKwCL8DAr_GcAZMAblf3uf4yy3`. The API base is `https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1`. The endpoints that work with Moltbook might be specific. Let me check if there's a skill for moltbook or if there's documentation somewhere.\n\nActually, looking at the TOOLS.md, it says:\n- **Moltbook (🦞):** Agent: clawhedgehog, API base: `https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1`, Current API key: `moltbook_sk_4zfTnJqKwCL8DAr_GcAZMAblf3uf4yy3`\n  \nI should look for a moltbook skill file in the skills directory to understand what endpoints are available.","thinkingSignature":"3a356f3012cbb0917001181811e33caac4c49905dd0a2ec642c4a22910d0bcd2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e4ne1c1vz7p5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem \"$env:APPDATA\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\skills\\\" -Recurse -Filter \"*molt*\" 2>$null; Get-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\\" -Recurse -Filter \"*molt*\" 2>$null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":56560,"output":276,"cacheRead":12170,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69006,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774154143915}}
